        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[how to authorize github]]></title>
            <link>https://kyphan38.github.io/web/blog/netrc</link>
            <guid>https://kyphan38.github.io/web/blog/netrc</guid>
            <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 15:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[Context]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="context">Context<a href="https://kyphan38.github.io/web/blog/netrc#context" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Context" title="Direct link to Context">​</a></h2>
<p>When working with GitHub, you may encounter an issue where you are prompted to enter your username and password every time you push changes</p>
<p>A solution to this is to set up a <code>.netrc</code> file, which store your credentials for logging in and authorizing GitHub</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="solution">Solution<a href="https://kyphan38.github.io/web/blog/netrc#solution" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Solution" title="Direct link to Solution">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="step-1-set-up-the-netrc-file">Step 1: Set up the .netrc file<a href="https://kyphan38.github.io/web/blog/netrc#step-1-set-up-the-netrc-file" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Step 1: Set up the .netrc file" title="Direct link to Step 1: Set up the .netrc file">​</a></h3>
<p>On a Mac, UNIX, or Linux, you can create the <code>.netrc</code> file using the following command:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">vim ~/.netrc</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p>Inside the <code>.netrc</code> file, adding the following lines as format:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">machine github.com</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">login &lt;your_username&gt;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">password &lt;your_credentials&gt;</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p>Example:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">machine github.com</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">login kyphan38</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">password ghp_lRC2nJdYVw1ws8shGfsquFIs9L1fx301VjQ1</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="step-2-set-file-permissions">Step 2: Set file permissions<a href="https://kyphan38.github.io/web/blog/netrc#step-2-set-file-permissions" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Step 2: Set file permissions" title="Direct link to Step 2: Set file permissions">​</a></h3>
<p>Since the .netrc file contains sensitive information, it's important to ensure that only your user has read/write access to it</p>
<p>To set the correct permissions, use the following command:</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chmod 600 ~/.netrc</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
